Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}圣天空战记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要坠入爱河每个人都会变得如此孤单?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正拥抱着比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切必定都是为了让我俩能绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用泪水来呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早就给了我 最宝贵的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,你在哪里?天野
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.79,0:01:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野学长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:01:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽翼的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.92,0:02:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根羽毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.23,0:02:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后,请别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根羽毛,感觉好像很哀伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别撞到地面了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走这条航道似乎有点困难
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们飞高点走别的路线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:02:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:02:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很明白这样会有多危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但唯有这条路才能不被\N寨巴哈发现,安全抵达弗雷特公国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也唯有你们才办得到,不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万别大意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要成功越过这座山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好让寨巴哈大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你也会来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在弗雷特等你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王姊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要阻止我也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要舍弃国家吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单惫你一个人,明明什么都办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再把我当孩子看了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您还有父王总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不考量我的心情,就擅自为我下决定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是为了你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我放弃继续学医也是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王族学习医术有什么用?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都想做些能够帮助其他人的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为王族只要在其位为民尽其本分就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任意妄为才是对人民的亵渎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢亚连!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了,王姊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了,王姊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神人乃背上长有翅膀之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚特兰提斯的末裔遭到诅咒的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?龙神人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神人?绝对不能接近龙神人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近龙神人者必死无疑,带来世界末日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭了亚特兰提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尼利亚?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您别这样,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梵大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人,好危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你一直说想看的耶,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,还是太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了,你好好看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜利之后的酒果然特别好暍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就要决战了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这个小队一定会率先攻入敌人主力阵营
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是法尼利亚的人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔卡斯\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争结束以后,你就要离开了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下想要重新锻炼自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这份恩情…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧,巴尔卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能继续精进武士之道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够再回到我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再回到法尼利亚来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚特兰提斯的末裔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的魔族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下,这里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您回避
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手,巴尔卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是魔人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我被那样的魔人夺去性命都无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是法尼利亚的巩恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会晓得我的名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚,当幻之月升至西山顶时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中注定的男人将会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我出生时的占卜预言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中注定?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命中注定的相会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中注定,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芭莉叶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芭莉叶,你愿意跟我走吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,巩恩大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梵的爸爸跟妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能迎娶龙神人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神人是使亚特兰提斯灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭到诅咒的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定会为法尼利亚招来祸患
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不同意这桩婚姻,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论传说为何,这都与芭莉叶无关
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是谁都无法拆散我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当有精神的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看,弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你的弟弟喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王,他叫什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵·法尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你不能让人见到你的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在时候来临前,你绝对不能将你的翅膀…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答应母后,别让母后难过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,母后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巩恩殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是没能赶上…巩恩殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭了,母后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会代替王兄成为国王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会成为像父王一样的坚强男子汉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请您别再哭了,母后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没多久后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后只身一人循着王兄的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯的步伐走进了森林中的龙巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔卡斯曾经进入森林里帮我去找寻过母后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却毫无所获
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后再也没有回到城里来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这些事告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那对翅膀…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵的翅膀…我很喜欢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很喜欢,很漂亮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有你和梅露露会说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是我跟梅露露一样笨吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看不到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的预见是一片浑沌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉没于混乱的底部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不让我看呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙影覆盖了未来的预见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,我们接下来要去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得弗雷特公国应该就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也说不上来,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西在吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是寨巴哈的那些隐形家伙吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里…他们的确就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,正前方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,梅露露,你们抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,右边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射得太偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明已经瞄准了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方似乎可以看见我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少说梦话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不让他死就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会从哪里攻击过来?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,正前方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用跑的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是河
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,梅露露,你们下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了,快下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林凡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟想要做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在水中就算隐形也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能看得到你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耍小聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在,动手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管你看不看得见,结果都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接把你给毁了如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙击队成功捕获目标
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将龙回收
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来人救救梵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快救救他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵啊,这就是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方出现浮游船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高兴能够再见到你,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你这混帐,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米盖尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太大意了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,你回答我啊,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下可不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷特公国的商船队接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒退,迪兰度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷特的船正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是现在让他们看到我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战计划就会被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打得正顺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回答我啊,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法止血
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟发生了什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详情以后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.59,0:19:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有医生在吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船只是往来于阿斯多利亚的"兰潘德"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与弗雷特的"戈达西姆"之间的贸易船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船上并没有能够医治这种重伤的医生…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是为了要救我,才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是迦迪斯的声音,对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来大家都在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁受伤了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这伤势…出血这么严重…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪斯,你还在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点帮他治疗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去亚连会撑不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我找不到医生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主,你应该行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.19,0:20:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾经学习过医术
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我只读过书本
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不曾…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望亚连队长活下去,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只有靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地鼠先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你将我的蓝色包包拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我出来,慢慢地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是老大有事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会马上宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想麻醉应该生效了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,你还是押住他,让他不要挣扎乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.07,0:21:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊,求求您
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您一定,一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要救救亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求您
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.17,0:22:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您曾经打从心底信赖过某个人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.81,0:22:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幻人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.71,0:23:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛国者?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝瞳的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:57.07,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月儿彼方蓝色探照灯照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:05.52,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降临的天使 你究竟是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:13.15,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的门扉即将开启　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:19.30,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放过这令人兴奋的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:21.66,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:26.67,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃烧般的神秘双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:30.51,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真无邪的笑容让我倾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:34.31,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深处的暗示只传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:38.32,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了无止尽的旅程
